milestones.description: Srinivas Venkataraghavan and Syed Abid Ali's 60-run partnership is the highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 40 between Underwood and Bob Taylor
Glenn Turner has scored 2 hundreds in ODIs, the most for NZ breaking Bevan Congdon's record
Srinivas Venkataraghavan has broken the record for most ODIs (3) as captain for IND, going past Ajit Wadekar
Hastings has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (10) for NZ, going past Glenn Turner
Syed Abid Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for IND, going past Engineer
Hastings and Glenn Turner's 65-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 33 between Bevan Congdon and Mark Burgess
Engineer and Gaekwad's 31-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Gavaskar and Gaekwad
Syed Abid Ali and Madan Lal's 55-run partnership is IND's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Syed Abid Ali and Brijesh Patel
Srinivas Venkataraghavan and Syed Abid Ali's 60-run partnership is IND's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 14 between Syed Abid Ali and Ashok Mankad
